{"tid":2374829,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大麻產業分析+討論區","createTime":"2021-01-21T13:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T05:53:24.000Z","uid":365423,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"614990703fcd2222746090e2b9987e82769662e6","tid":2374829,"uid":365423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:45:02.000Z","msg":"大麻目前在全球大多數國家仍被視為非法毒品，不過隨著歐洲和美國逐漸開放管制，合法醫療用大麻和娛樂用大麻需求都在快速增長中。在一個越來越讓人沮喪、高壓、睡眠失調和精神疾病的世界，越來越多人可能會需要大麻相關的用品，對於政府來說，大麻產業合法化後也可能會貢獻顯著的稅收和就業，對於債台高築的地方政府有非常大的誘因進一步合法化大麻公司讓他們成為稅收機器。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.visualcapitalist.com/european-cbd-landscape-in-2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.visualcapitalist.com%2Feuropean-cbd-landscape-in-2020%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=0600ec68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.visualcapitalist.com/european-cbd-landscape-in-2020/</a><br />\n<br />\n2020Q4財報中，Aphria CEO看好美國大選結果可能會改變聯邦大麻法規，公司期望在民主黨領導下會更快做出改變和決策。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QAePHrtKQic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQAePHrtKQic&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=67cecfff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QAePHrtKQic</a><br />\n<br />\n美國早前有五個州投票通過合法化娛樂用和醫用大麻，全美已經有15個州大麻全面合法，36個州醫用大麻合法。支持合法化的趨勢隨著年輕人成為社會主流會越來越高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDczgKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDczgKu.png&h=dfdc8f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究機構New Frontier Data預估大麻銷售到2025年會成長到415億，比2020年銷售規模再多出一倍。根據ResearchAndMarkets的數據，到2027年，全球大麻二酚（CBD）油市場和整個CBD消費者健康市場價值可能高達1230億美元，CAGR為25.6％。全球大麻飲料市場到2027年，其價值將達到85億美元。這個市場在2019年的價值僅為3.674億美元，意味著其CAGR 為50.9％ 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TafH94A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTafH94A.png&h=6c093086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>大麻業兩大巨頭Aphria與Tilray合併</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n加拿大大麻生產商Aphria與Tilray在2020年底合併。兩家產品的種類橫跨藥用與娛樂，包含大麻電子煙、大麻飲料、零食等。估算大麻零售市佔率會到17.3%。<br />\n<br />\n合併後的公司在加拿大成人用大麻的銷售，也領先Canopy Growth和Aurora。大麻行業目前相對分散，未來很可能會持續出現大吃小整併集中化的趨勢，主要是因為合法的生產成本和通路優勢若拉開差距，對落後者會更難追上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xsvzEt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xsvzEt.png&h=486c4e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAphria 在去年十二月以3億美金併購了美國最大的獨立精釀啤酒公司Sweetwater（SW），SW的啤酒品牌420系列能模擬大麻口味。Aphria收購SW能建立和擴大Aphria在美國的業務，SW本身在美國27個州都有通路包括餐廳、獨立零售和連鎖店。在美國大麻合法化的進程下，可以更快速地推展銷售的業務。<br />\n<br />\nTilray則是在2019年就收購了大麻食品生產商Manitoba Harvest。在沒有太大重疊的大麻製品領域與Aphria有互補的效果。Aphria 2019年收購了在德國市場領先的醫藥通路商CC Pharma，Tilray則在葡萄牙有獲歐盟EU GMP認證的大麻歐盟生產與出口許可。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>大麻股的風險</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大麻產業受政策變化影響很大，而且股價波動劇烈，Tilray在2018年兩個月暴漲5倍，Aurora升386%，但是因為生產過剩與過度樂觀的市場情緒，2019年下跌了90%以上。相較之下，APHA的財務狀況比其他大麻股穩健得多。<br />\n<br />\n此外，大麻黑市的佔比達6成，合法的只有4成。合法大麻的價格競爭力也遠不如黑市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owYbjbp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowYbjbp.png&h=84871eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://midasletter.com/2020/01/cannabis-shares-black-market-overproduction-and-slow-legalization-trouble-the-marijuana-market/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmidasletter.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fcannabis-shares-black-market-overproduction-and-slow-legalization-trouble-the-marijuana-market%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=546ab872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://midasletter.com/2020/01/cannabis-shares-black-market-overproduction-and-slow-legalization-trouble-the-marijuana-market/</a>"},{"pid":"041657825acca0e672f6034604503f31c06fd193","tid":2374829,"uid":365423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:58:11.000Z","msg":"GrowGeneration (GRWG)賣大麻種植輔助用具（水培用品、土壤、植物生長燈等）以及擁有園藝用品的連鎖店，在大麻合法化的趨勢下，淘金時賣鏟子的公司營收增長非常顯著，股價一年升十倍。另外可以留意大麻ETF &mdash;&mdash; ETFMG Alternative Harvest ETF (代號MJ)。"},{"pid":"f991376a11c424a32d9150b0345897e105f3ac5d","tid":2374829,"uid":169845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"Pish 二月係咪有大麻法案？"},{"pid":"488f06878402db1db3459bbb6ebb849cd69b63af","tid":2374829,"uid":72116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f991376a11c424a32d9150b0345897e105f3ac5d","tid":2374829,"uid":169845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"Pish 二月係咪有大麻法案？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"一月30"},{"pid":"ca1af7f096e209e49f9d6834f0285c4f33dfe3fe","tid":2374829,"uid":199864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"全部大麻股應該又黎個大回調<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12a1650d599f5e5816c4d7dcd5aabe0c8b18900","tid":2374829,"uid":169845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca1af7f096e209e49f9d6834f0285c4f33dfe3fe","tid":2374829,"uid":199864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"全部大麻股應該又黎個大回調<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"Why?"},{"pid":"23f4cdfb0a890af430a9ff2ce3635bf61b728597","tid":2374829,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:32:30.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"027e29d7233afa8b17cd34a115cd5dec78d3811a","tid":2374829,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4d519ccff1c098e7ee8d4e83039743a3abe9fa03","tid":2374829,"uid":373001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:45:07.000Z","msg":"Sndl<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7f72b2885009aa5dcd9e1504d29bd0c102932f","tid":2374829,"uid":4